621
01:13:56,990 --> 01:13:57,890
Patch?

622
01:13:59,100 --> 01:14:00,150
Patch?

623
01:14:03,670 --> 01:14:06,160
Espera, Patch. Espera.

624
01:14:09,070 --> 01:14:10,560
Cachorrito...

625
01:14:26,320 --> 01:14:28,850
Quién te lastimó, Patch? Quién te lastimó?

626
