<i>En Gales, el gobernador...</i>

627
01:17:17,760 --> 01:17:19,290
<i>Antes que David comenzara...</i>

628
01:17:44,250 --> 01:17:45,520
<i>No luce nada bien.</i>

629
01:17:47,760 --> 01:17:51,630
<i>Porque David Lange no lograba 
