643
01:20:58,420 --> 01:20:59,510
Nick!

644
01:21:40,360 --> 01:21:41,720
<i>Central para Peter Roger.</i>

645
01:21:42,190 --> 01:21:44,530
<i>Estamos sobrevolando el lugar ahora.</i>

646
01:21:44,560 --> 01:21:49,190
<i>Estamos sobrevolando la calle Taki
