677
01:25:37,190 --> 01:25:41,490
<i>Estamos todos aquí, abuela. Esperándote.</i>

678
01:25:42,700 --> 01:25:44,060
<i>Philipp vino para acá.</i>

679
01:25:44,900 --> 01:25:46,270
<i>Y Ani.</i>

680
01:25:46,740 --> 01:25:47,830
<i>Y Jason.</i>

681
01:25:50,010 --> 01:25:51,700
